title: Sans-Serif Font ID request
content:
I came here from webdesignerdepot.com and I'm hoping someone can please help me ID this font.  
I've tried sites like whatthefont.com with no success.

The second picture is 'photoshopped'. I threw it in incase it helps.

The text reads "FloRES"

comments.content: Not quite what I was looking for. Thanks for the help

My first thought was that it's a custom drawing, but it's finally **[Wankstaberg Battles](http://web.archive.org/web/20131106094637/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Dafont-2&ffam=Wankstaberg%20Battles%20-%20Regular%20Italic&fid=307b1d5b393645c400bca9b3c7a8157c&fsize=60&text=FloRES&wrap=2)** by Måns Grebäck (free for personal use) - somehow expanded
